import { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import CountriesService from "../services/CountryService,"; import {Table,Menu,Icon} from 'semantic-ui-react' import React from "react"; import 'semantic-ui-css/semantic.min.css' export default function CountryList(){ const[countries,setCountries]=useState([]) useEffect(() => { let countriesService=new CountriesService() countriesService.getCountries().then(result=>setCountries(result.data.data)) }) return (
Name Region Flag { countries.map( country=> {country.name} {country.capital} {countries.region} ) } 1 2 3 4
